1.2
log
@* games went off to ports/games/bsdgames
* don't install isakmpd or ctm samples
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: init.c,v 1.7 2002/07/18 07:13:57 pjanzen Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: init.c,v 1.4 1995/04/28 23:49:19 mycroft Exp $	*/

